{"tid":1416153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺聽KOL之前 入嚟聽返天琦一言先","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:59:15.000Z","uid":54125,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"141fef0968bd08c9e72b16b8e0e35b92f53227e1","tid":1416153,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢句我哋講咗大半個月，突然個個都話唔好嗌<br />\n到底係出於乜嘢令你覺得<br />\n畀人話係港獨就會失敗？<br />\n<br />\n中共最驚係咩<br />\n係驚人民有信念<br />\n最初發起呢個信念嘅人已經被判暴動罪<br />\n佢無得再拉<br />\n佢哋可以做嘅，就係瓦解你哋嘅信念。<br />\n<br />\n喺你覺得動搖嘅時候，請聽返天琦一言<br />\n點解，我哋需要光復香港<br />\n點解我哋需要時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4272cbec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},{"pid":"b83f40e96c3691cf7bb35e3889c906d341dd01df","tid":1416153,"uid":66566,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人擁護我就反對 敵人反對我就擁護</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"93a5b648287d54761608535628b06edd0863c1af","tid":1416153,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f1bcfcf7bef224444532dbf94ee0c4c972eb827f","tid":1416153,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4954f2035aa9895cd05ded5ea7ed0b4660b05ee","tid":1416153,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"48aa09a7a7a200961119d6bfa487d770eebed0b7","tid":1416153,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:38.00